Privacy Policy for SAP Quiz

Effective date: January 14th, 2025

At SAP Quiz, accessible from SAP Quiz, we prioritize the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy document outlines the types of information that is collected and recorded by SAP Quiz and how we use it.

1. Information We Collect

When you use SAP Quiz, we may collect the following types of information:

Personal Information: We do not require personal information for the basic functioning of the app. However, if you use certain features, such as signing in with your Google account or saving your results, you may be asked to provide personal information like your name, email, etc.
Usage Data: We may collect information about how the app is accessed and used. This data may include your device’s internet protocol address, browser type, version, and pages of our app that you visit, time and date of your visit, and other diagnostic data.
Device Information: We may collect information about your device, such as its model, operating system version, unique device identifiers, and mobile network information.
2. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

To provide and maintain the app, including monitoring the usage of the app.
To improve, personalize, and expand our app’s features and content.
To understand and analyze usage patterns in order to improve the app’s functionality.
To communicate with you, either directly or through our partners, including providing customer support and sending you updates or other information.
3. Third-Party Services

SAP Quiz may use third-party services that may collect information used to identify you. These third parties include:

Google Analytics: To track and analyze app usage and performance.
Firebase: To provide app functionalities such as notifications, authentication, and analytics.
These third-party services have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to read them to understand how your information is handled.

4. Data Security

We take reasonable precautions to protect your personal information. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

5. Sharing Your Information

We do not share your personal information with third parties except as described in this Privacy Policy or as required by law. We may share aggregated, non-identifiable data with third parties for analytical purposes.

6. Children’s Privacy

SAP Quiz is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected information from a child under 13, please contact us so that we can take appropriate action.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: desync2023@gmail.com
